{"type":null,"faqId":45310,"title":"荣耀盒子M321的手机微信推片有什么用，如何使用？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>手机微信推片指的是可以通过添加盒子的微信公众号，在微信公众号上搜索节目，并将节目推送到电视上播放。具体操作如下：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164836\" style=\"width:1.5520834in;height:1.5520834in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>您可以进入盒子“</span><span class=\"s1\">应用 &gt; 帮助 &gt; 使用技巧</span><span>”，选择“</span><span class=\"s1\">创意遥控器，使用更有趣</span><span>”。查看到该二维码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">方式一：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 1  </span><span>扫描二维码，添加盒子的微信公众号“</span><span class=\"s1\">华为荣耀盒子M321</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 2  </span><span>打开微信公众号的对话框，输入您想看的节目名称。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 3  </span><span>在收到的回复中，点击节目图片。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 4  </span><span>在打开的节目详情页面中，选择“</span><span class=\"s1\">推送到荣耀盒子M321</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>此时，电视将播放该节目。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">方式二：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 1  </span><span>扫描二维码，添加盒子的微信公众号“</span><span class=\"s1\">华为荣耀盒子M321</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 2  </span><span>打开微信公众号的对话框，选择“</span><span class=\"s1\">应用 &gt; 节目导航</span><span>”</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 3  </span><span>在打开的节目导航中选择您想看的节目，选择“</span><span class=\"s1\">推送到荣耀盒子M321</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>此时，电视将播放该节目。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":244,"faqType":"在线播放","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"831","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Online-Play","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442556872000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M321,MediaQ M321-20","visitedTimes":13,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"手机微信,推片,荣耀盒子","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}